      <Math mode="display" tex="\begin{CD}\bullet @&gt;{v}&gt;{}&gt;\bullet\\&#10;@V{g}V{}V@V{}V{f}V\\&#10;\bullet @&gt;{{\vbox to 0.0pt{\vss\hbox{}\vskip 15.1767pt}}}&gt;{{\vbox to 0.0pt{%&#10;\vskip-5.16pt\hbox{}\vss}}}&gt;\bullet\end{CD}" text="commutative-diagram[[bullet, rightarrowfill@ ^ v, bullet], [g downarrow absent, , absent downarrow f, , ], [bullet, (rightarrowfill@ ^ []) _ [], bullet]]" xml:id="S0.Ex4.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMArray meaning="commutative-diagram">
            <XMRow>

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex15">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\par\tikzpicture[xscale=3,yscale=1.6]\par\node(12)at(2,-1){};\par\node(21)at(1%&#10;,-2){};\node(22)at(2,-2){};\node(23)at(3,-2){};\par\node(31)at(1,-3){};\node(3%&#10;2)at(2,-3){};\node(33)at(3,-3){};\par\node(42)at(2,-4){};\par\par\par\draw[-&gt;]%&#10;(21)--(22);\draw[-&gt;](23)--(22);\par\draw[-&gt;](31)--(32);\draw[-&gt;](33)--(32);%&#10;\par\par\draw[-&gt;](21)--(31);\par\draw[-&gt;](22)--(32);\draw[-&gt;](32)--(42);\par%&#10;\draw[-&gt;](23)--(33);\par\par\par\draw[-&gt;](12)--(21)node[right=1pt,midway,scale%&#10;=.75]{};\draw[-&gt;](12)--(23);\par\draw[-&gt;](31)--(42)node[right=1pt,midway,scale%&#10;=.75]{};\draw[-&gt;](33)--(42);\par\par\node at(2,-1.55)[scale=.9]{{\textcircled{%&#10;\scriptsize{1}}}};\node at(1.5,-2.5)[scale=.9]{{\textcircled{\scriptsize{2}}}}%&#10;;\node at(2.5,-2.5)[scale=.9]{{\textcircled{\scriptsize{3}}}};\node at(1.75,-3%&#10;.4)[scale=.9]{{\textcircled{\scriptsize{4}}}};\node at(2.25,-3.4)[scale=.9]{{%&#10;\textcircled{\scriptsize{5}}}};\par" xml:id="S0.Ex15.m1">
        <XMath>
          <ERROR class="undefined">{tikzpicture}</ERROR>
          <XMWrap>
            <XMTok role="OPEN" stretchy="false">[</XMTok>
            <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">x</XMTok>
            <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">s</XMTok>
            <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">c</XMTok>
            <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">a</XMTok>
            <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">l</XMTok>
            <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">e</XMTok>
            <XMTok meaning="equals" role="RELOP">=</XMTok>

          </XMWrap>
          <XMTok role="PUNCT">;</XMTok>
        </XMath>
      </Math>
    </equation>
  </para>

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex19">
      <Math mode="display" tex="u^{\times}{{\mskip 8.0mu \longrightarrow\mskip-25.5mu {}^{\sim}\mskip 17.0mu }%&#10;}u^{*}{\mathsf{R}}u_{*}u^{\times}{\longrightarrow}u^{*}=u^{!}." text="u ^ * longrightarrow ^ similar-to u ^ * * R * u _ * * u ^ * longrightarrow u ^ * = u ^ factorial" xml:id="S0.Ex19.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.Ex19.m1.1"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex19.m1.1">
                <XMTok meaning="multirelation"/>
                <XMApp rpadding="4.4pt">
                  <XMTok role="SUPERSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                  <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">u</XMTok>
                  <XMTok fontsize="70%" meaning="times" role="MULOP">×</XMTok>
                </XMApp>
                <XMTok name="longrightarrow" role="ARROW" rpadding="-14.2pt">⟶</XMTok>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok role="SUPERSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="pre4"/>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok role="SUPERSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                      <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">u</XMTok>
                      <XMTok fontsize="70%" meaning="times" role="MULOP">*</XMTok>
                    </XMApp>
                    <XMTok fontsize="70%" meaning="similar-to" name="sim" role="RELOP">∼</XMTok>
                  </XMApp>
                  <XMTok font="sansserif" role="UNKNOWN">R</XMTok>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                    <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">u</XMTok>
                    <XMTok fontsize="70%" meaning="times" role="MULOP">*</XMTok>
                  </XMApp>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok role="SUPERSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                    <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">u</XMTok>
                    <XMTok fontsize="70%" meaning="times" role="MULOP">×</XMTok>
                  </XMApp>
                </XMApp>
                <XMTok name="longrightarrow" role="ARROW">⟶</XMTok>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok role="SUPERSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>

                  <XMTok fontsize="70%" meaning="times" role="MULOP">*</XMTok>
                </XMApp>

                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok role="SUPERSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                  <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">u</XMTok>

  <para xml:id="p41">
    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex32">
      <Math mode="display" tex="{\mathsf{R}}u_{*}(E{\otimes^{\mathsf{L}}_{{{\mskip-1.0mu }\&lt;X}}}u^{*}){%&#10;\xrightarrow{}}{\!\operatorname{{\textup{via}}}\&gt;u^{*}\eta_{1}}{\mathsf{R}}u_{%&#10;*}(E{\otimes^{\mathsf{L}}_{{{\mskip-1.0mu }\&lt;X}}}u^{*}{\mathsf{R}}u_{*}u^{*})." text="R * u _ * * (E (tensor-product ^ L) _ ([\less] * X) u ^ *) absent@(rightarrow) [via]@(u ^ * * eta _ 1 * R * u _ *) * (E (tensor-product ^ L) _ ([\less] * X) u ^ *) * R * u _ * * u ^ *" xml:id="S0.Ex32.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.Ex32.m1.1"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex32.m1.1">
                <XMApp role="ARROW" rpadding="-1.7pt">
                  <XMTok meaning="absent" role="OVERACCENT"/>
                  <XMTok name="rightarrow" role="ARROW">→</XMTok>
                </XMApp>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                  <XMTok font="sansserif" role="UNKNOWN">R</XMTok>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                    <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">u</XMTok>
                    <XMTok fontsize="70%" meaning="times" role="MULOP">*</XMTok>
                  </XMApp>
                  <XMDual>

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex53">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\psi(p,u)(G)\colon f^{\times}G{{\mskip 8.0mu \longrightarrow\mskip-25.5mu {}^{%&#10;\sim}\mskip 17.0mu }}u^{\times}p^{\times}G=u^{\times}p^{!}G{\xrightarrow{}}{\!%&#10;\psi(u)p^{!}}u^{!}p^{!}G=(p,u)^{!}G" text="psi * open-interval@(p, u) * G colon f ^ * * G longrightarrow ^ similar-to u ^ * * p ^ * * G = u ^ * * p ^ factorial * G absent@(rightarrow) psi * u * p ^ factorial * u ^ factorial * p ^ factorial * G = (open-interval@(p, u)) ^ factorial * G" xml:id="S0.Ex53.m1">
        <XMath>

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex127">
      <Math mode="display" tex="E{\otimes^{\mathsf{L}}_{{{\mskip-1.0mu }\&lt;X}}}k(x)\cong{\mathsf{R}}\iota_{x*}{%&#10;\mskip-1.0mu }\big{(}\iota_{x}^{*}E{\otimes^{\mathsf{L}}_{{X_{x}}}}\widetilde{%&#10;\kappa(x)}\big{)}." text="(E (tensor-product ^ L) _ ([\less] * X) k) * x approximately-equals R * iota _ (list@(x, *)) * (((iota _ x) ^ * * E) (tensor-product ^ L) _ X _ x widetilde@(kappa * x))" xml:id="S0.Ex127.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.Ex127.m1.5"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex127.m1.5">

                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMApp meaning="tensor-product" role="MULOP">
